<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{alertTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
        }
        
        .header.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
        }
        
        .header.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
        }
        
        .header.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .alert-notice {
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.error {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left-color: #ef4444;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.error p {
            color: #991b1b;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.warning {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left-color: #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.warning p {
            color: #92400e;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.success {
            background-color: #dcfce7;
            border-left-color: #22c55e;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.success p {
            color: #15803d;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.info {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left-color: #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .alert-notice.info p {
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .alert-notice p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button.error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.info {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .timestamp-info {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        .timestamp-info p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                padding: 14px 28px;
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header {{alertType}}">
            <h1>
                {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}üö®{{/if}}
                {{#if eq alertType 'warning'}}‚ö†Ô∏è{{/if}}
                {{#if eq alertType 'success'}}‚úÖ{{/if}}
                {{#if eq alertType 'info'}}‚ÑπÔ∏è{{/if}}
                System Alert
            </h1>
            <p>{{alertTitle}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            {{#if recipientName}}
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{recipientName}},
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="message">
                {{alertMessage}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="alert-notice {{alertType}}">
                <p>
                    <span class="alert-icon">
                        {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}üö®{{/if}}
                        {{#if eq alertType 'warning'}}‚ö†Ô∏è{{/if}}
                        {{#if eq alertType 'success'}}‚úÖ{{/if}}
                        {{#if eq alertType 'info'}}‚ÑπÔ∏è{{/if}}
                    </span>
                    <strong>{{alertTitle}}:</strong> 
                    {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}This issue requires immediate attention.{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'warning'}}Please review this important information.{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'success'}}This update has been successfully completed.{{/if}}
                    {{#if eq alertType 'info'}}This is an informational update for your awareness.{{/if}}
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timestamp-info">
                <p><strong>Alert Details:</strong></p>
                <p>Date & Time: {{formatDate timestamp 'long'}}</p>
                <p>Alert Type: {{alertType}}</p>
                <p>System: {{companyName}} Platform</p>
            </div>
            
            {{#if actionUrl}}
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button {{alertType}}">
                    {{#if actionText}}{{actionText}}{{else}}Learn More{{/if}}
                </a>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="message">
                {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}
                <strong>We're addressing this issue:</strong><br>
                We know how frustrating technical issues can be, especially when you're in the flow of learning. Our entire team is focused on resolving this quickly so you can get back to what matters most - your progress. We truly appreciate your patience and are here to support you through this.
                {{else if eq alertType 'warning'}}
                <strong>Please note this important information:</strong><br>
                We're sharing this important update because we respect your time and want you to plan accordingly. Transparency is important to us, and we believe you deserve to know what's happening with your learning platform.
                {{else if eq alertType 'success'}}
                <strong>Great news to share! üéâ</strong><br>
                We love celebrating positive updates with our learning community. Thank you for being part of what makes {{companyName}} special - your engagement and feedback help us continuously improve.
                {{else}}
                <strong>Keeping you informed:</strong><br>
                We believe in keeping you informed about your learning platform. This update helps ensure you have the latest information to make the most of your {{companyName}} experience.
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if eq alertType 'error'}}
            <div class="message">
                <strong>What you can do:</strong>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                    <li>Check our status page for real-time updates</li>
                    <li>Try refreshing the page or logging out and back in</li>
                    <li>Contact support if the issue persists</li>
                    <li>Follow our social media for the latest updates</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>{{companyName}} System Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This is an automated system notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 